### Variables
@host = http://localhost:5051
@tenantId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
@customerId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@reservationId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# CUSTOMERS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Registrar cliente
POST {{host}}/customers
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carlos Mendoza",
  "phone": "3001234567",
  "email": "carlos@example.com"
}

###

### Listar clientes
GET {{host}}/customers?page=1&pageSize=10
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Obtener cliente por ID
GET {{host}}/customers/{{customerId}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Actualizar cliente
PUT {{host}}/customers/{{customerId}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carlos Mendoza Actualizado",
  "phone": "3009876543",
  "email": "carlos.nuevo@example.com"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# RESERVATIONS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Crear reserva
POST {{host}}/reservations
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "reservationDate": "2025-02-15",
  "timeSlot": "10:00:00"
}

###

### Confirmar reserva
POST {{host}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/confirm
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Cancelar reserva
POST {{host}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/cancel
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Marcar llegada
POST {{host}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/arrived
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Completar reserva
POST {{host}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/complete
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Reagendar reserva
POST {{host}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}/reschedule
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newDate": "2025-02-20",
  "newTimeSlot": "14:00:00"
}

###

### Obtener reserva por ID
GET {{host}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Listar reservas
GET {{host}}/reservations?page=1&pageSize=10
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Reservas de un cliente
GET {{host}}/customers/{{customerId}}/reservations
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# AVAILABILITY & AGENDA
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Consultar disponibilidad
GET {{host}}/reservations/availability?date=2025-02-15
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Agenda del día
GET {{host}}/agenda?date=2025-02-15
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Resumen de reservas
GET {{host}}/reservations/summary?from=2025-02-01&to=2025-02-28
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###
